data.description: Such great space!  This brick ranch home in east Salina checks all of the boxes!  Generous living and bedroom spaces on both floors.  Super for entertaining and family time.  Kitchen features brand new granite countertops and appliances.  Breakfast bar and fabulous dining space, access to the back patio for those fall evenings!  Fireplace in the dining area is another great feature.  Main floor bathrooms also have nice updates.  Amazing storage and built-ins at every turn!  2nd floor has 3 large bedrooms, another updated full bath, and a library/office area.   House features a full basement with 2 large finished rooms and another fireplace.  Great yard with privacy fence and brick patio.  Additional 3rd garage has been added for storage or extra parking.  Generous space, fabulous location, super options!
